{
  "stem": "27507.2",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And we lived all in one quite big and darkish apartment, where one room was as well two Russian women were living.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Those Russian women, I was told-- I think they were-- they were as well [INAUDIBLE] women.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And of course, the Russians would-- would confiscate a flat or a part of a flat to put their own people.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And so we were living with those Russians in one flat.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And as for-- and in eastern Poland in those days, the situation was totally unclear.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "It was not obvious what was going to happen.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the Russian authorities demanded of people that they declare themselves whether they want to retain the Polish citizenship or whether they want to remain the Soviet citizens.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And it was pretty-- whether they want to became-- to become Soviet citizens.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And it was pretty clear that there were consequences.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "But nobody knew exactly what consequences were going to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my parents obviously didn't want to agree to become Soviet citizens, because as far as we were concerned, it could have been forever.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "But what happened was that those people who declared that they want to become-- that they want to accept Soviet nationality were left more or less in peace.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "Those, however, who didn't want to, who said that they want to keep their Polish nationality, were later on deported in great numbers to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "They were-- they basically prepared for them transports, cattle trucks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they took them in great numbers to Siberia.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And of course, nobody knew how it was going to end ever.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And of course, the fear of Siberia was probably bigger than of anything else.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
